svg.title: The Double Doughnut: A Design Process Model

cc:Work.dc:title: The Double Doughnut: A Design Process Model
cc:Work.dc:description: A model illustrating a 'lean' and cyclical design process comprised of two parts: problem identification and solution generation. Problem generation consists of three stages: exploration, analysis and insight. Solution generation consists of 3 stages: ideation, synthesis and evaluation.
